title: #97: Vegetable Face (Mac Danzig)
itunes:title: Vegetable Face with Mac Danzig
description: Mac Danzig met me at the Comedy Store to talk about veganism. He's a UFC fighter and 100% Vegan. It's an odd choice for a fighter. Come listen in on the conversation. He's a really chill guy. Not like the normal vegans who shove their views down your throat so you don't have room to eat burgers.
